snippet.title: 'Humanity's Phase Shift', Daniel Schmachtenberger
snippet.description:
Daniel Schmachtenberger is a futurist, evolutionary philosopher and strategist, and social engineer.

This conversation with David Fuller of Rebel Wisdom looks at the growing civilisation-level crisis that we are beginning to see around us, and looks at what a genuine 'phase shift' for human progress might look like.

Rebel Wisdom is a platform for the biggest ideas around. 
http://www.rebelwisdom.co.uk/

Rebel Wisdom is running workshops for men and women to get a direct experience of the ideas in our films: https://rebelwisdom.co.uk/events

Find us on iTunes and Spotify, or visit rebelwisdom.podbean.com to download Rebel Wisdom as an audio podcast.
